* 5T OTA — single-transistor PMOS current-mirror load (classic) — GF180MCU-D
* Devices: nfet_03v3 (3.3 V NMOS), pfet_03v3 (3.3 V PMOS)
.subckt {{netlist_name}} gnda vdda vinn vinp vout Ib
* NMOS diff pair
XM1 vout  vinn net2 gnda nfet_03v3 l={{ M1_L }}u w={{ M1_W }}u m={{ M1_M }}
XM2 net1  vinp net2 gnda nfet_03v3 l={{ M1_L }}u w={{ M1_W }}u m={{ M1_M }}
* PMOS mirror load — single transistor per branch
XM5 vout  net1 vdda vdda pfet_03v3 l={{ M5_L }}u w={{ M5_W }}u m={{ M5_M }}
XM6 net1  net1 vdda vdda pfet_03v3 l={{ M5_L }}u w={{ M5_W }}u m={{ M5_M }}
* Tail current source (M3) mirrors bias reference (M4)
XM3 net2  net3 gnda gnda nfet_03v3 l={{ M3_L }}u w={{ M3_W }}u m={{ M3_M }}
XM4 net3  net3 gnda gnda nfet_03v3 l={{ M4_L }}u w={{ M4_W }}u m={{ M4_M }}
I0  vdda  net3 'IBIAS'
Rdum_Ib Ib gnda 1
.ends {{netlist_name}}
